(168, 171, 'Mobile Family Health History Tool for Teens', 1358312400, 1358312400, 1365566400, 1, 'Create mobile app for family health history collection based on My Family Health Portrait (https://familyhistory.hhs.gov) but geared toward teen audience. Goal is to encourage and enable teens to collect their family health history information and to share this information with their doctor, as well as other family members.', '', 'Prototype', 'Collaborative'),
