(172, 175, 'Mobile Electronic Data Capture', 1360126800, 1360126800, 1370232000, 3, 'Goals\r\nSetting up a sandbox to explore mobile data collection tools, specifically the use case where the workflow corresponds to directly replacing paper based instruments\r\n\r\nChallenges\r\nSecurity and privacy requirements for electronic data capture solutions on mobile devices\r\n\r\nOpportunities\r\nSuccess in this area may result in approved contemporary solutions for data collection in international work\r\n', '', 'Prototype', 'External'),
