(179, 182, 'CDC Microtasking Wiki', 1364529600, 1364529600, 1372564800, 2, 'The information about the proposed CDC microtasking project is housed currently on the OPHPR SharePoint site with limited viewership. Since this project has gained interest both in CDC and externally, setting up a wiki page for microtasking would concrete this idea as our own but more importantly, educate about and promote the project for funding. I envision the wiki being the first stop for anyone interested in learning more. The association with the lab is a boon for the project developers because we want to ensure CDC is credited with the effort and because of the stellar reputation of your products and services.', 'No', 'Prototype', 'External'),
