(183, 186, 'OADC Mobile App Testing ', 1367208000, 1367208000, 1375243200, 0, 'The goal of the App Testing Project is to allow stakeholders of OADC mobile applications to download and test mobile apps on their personal mobile devices. This will be accomplished by the lab posting .ipa files so app testers can download them on the fly instead of having a designated OADC resource sit with them and manually install the app. This will make the OADC app testing process more efficient as app testers can download the app builds in a timelier manner and spend more time testing the app than trying to download it.', 'No', 'Prototype', 'Collaborative'),
