(187, 190, 'PUBLIC HEALTH ALERTING REPOSITORY SYSTEM (PHARS) TESTING', 1371009600, 1371009600, 1380513600, 2, 'The PHARS platform will be available for CDC programs algorithms to be utilized for delivery of actionable recommendation guidelines to a clinical setting at the point-of-care (Strengthening public health and healthcare integration for population health improvements).  The purpose of this request is to test the connectivity of an external EHR System (GE Centricity at Lehigh Valley Health Network, LVHN) to the PHARS platform where public health web services have been implemented as CDS tools with the ability to process discrete patient data elements within an algorithm resulting in a dynamically generate HTML page to be view by the clinician.', '', 'Prototype', 'External'),
