(46, 43, 'Passord Reset for Robert Perry - 6/6/2011\r\nEmailed Michele Renshaw for feedback - 5/9/2012\r\nOld PoC was Michele Renshaw, she said Guy Faler is the new PoC\r\nFeedback from Guy: "We are using this VM.  It hosts our IMATS Test-Drive instance.  This instance allows prospective users of IMATS to try out the system before enrolling in SAMS and entering real data into the production version of the system.  It is an important capability for us and we would like to keep it."\r\nExpired - June 2013-  Contacted Guy to see if renewal is needed.\r\n\r\n\r\nDr. Savel,\r\n\r\nI just confirmed with Jaideep that we still need the IMATS Test Drive VM.\r\n\r\nReceived email on June 3, 2013 at 10:49 AM from Guy Faler.\r\n\r\nSorry for the large attachment but the map below shows partners that are using IMATS.  We are very pleased by the uptake and feel like we are just getting started.  Iâ€™d like to mention again that the IMATS Test Drive is a very important piece of our strategy to increase adoption of IMATS.  We are very happy for the support we get from the IRDU and, trust me, we tell everyone about it!\r\n\r\nThanks.\r\n', ''),
