(69, 66, 'Emailed Pamela Jones for feedback 5/9/12\r\nArchived per Pam Jones.\r\nVM: Lvp-NCIRD1-W7E1\r\nFeedback received on 5/14:\r\nHere are some comments from the developers who used the VM.\r\n\r\n1.	Good to know this type of support exist for testing applications and simulating certain environments\r\n2.	I thought connection was very slow that it would drag the mouse and application along the screen. \r\n3.	Sometimes it would not connect at all\r\n4.	Too many steps to connect\r\n\r\nOnce again thanks for your support.\r\n\r\nPamela\r\n\r\n', ''),
