(132, 129, '4/22/13 - Tom and Brian met with Kevin Webb, Darryl Owens, Bob Thomas and Nimesh Patel in the Lab to set up Apple Developer accounts. Engagement will use Lab macs to test app deployment. They wish to use the AppLab as well.\r\n\r\nEngagement may be renewed based on findings in initial 6 months.\r\n\r\n2 iPad 3 16GB Black (barcodes) 225717 and 225718\r\n2 Apple Care Licensing\r\n\r\nSpoke to Kevin Webb on 4/3/13, wants to use app lab to test their iPad app.', ''),
