(153, 150, 'We had a reminder that we needed to touch base with you by the end of February 2013 about continuing our access to the Informatics Lab for use on our Mobile Framework System.  We continue to have need for the environment that we have setup in the lab as we use it for pre-release testing of mobile applications with our internal customers as well as other OPDIVs (e.g., FDA).  We are in the process of testing out a v2.0 update to the mobile framework that should be released in the next 1-2 months and having access to the Informatics Lab will be critical to our testing.\r\n\r\nWe would like to request that our existing users/permissions be extended for an additional 6 months to support this project\r\n---- APPROVED on 2/19/2013 for 6 month extension.', ''),
